====== H2351: חוּץ ======

===== Source =====

or (shortened)   ; (both forms feminine in the plural) from an unused root meaning to sever;

===== Meaning =====

properly,  separate by a wall , i.e.  outside ,  outdoors

===== Definitions =====

  - separate by a wall
  - outside
  - outdoors

===== Usage =====

abroad, field, forth, highway, more, out(-side, -ward), street, without.
